            "text": "<ul><li>What is the Word?</li><li>Why spread the Word?</li><li>How do I spread the Word?</li><li>What if I’m hesitant to spread the Word?</li><li>How do I follow up after I spread the Word? </li></ul>",
            "align_text_block": "inherit",
